title: Star Wars Omnibus Mega Pack
description:
Because why not? But you have to say it like the guy doing the voiceover for a monster truck commercial...

Sunday, Sunday, Sunday! Only at The Pirate Bay, it's the Star Wars Omnibus MEGA PAAAAAACK!

There are more of these, if I find them one at a time I'll upload them individually, if I come across a bunch at once I'll do another MEGA PAAAAACK!

Grab them all, grab the ones you're missing, or totally ignore them because you already have all the single issues.

Without further opening crawl, here you go! 13,083 pages of Star Wars omnibuses.... omnibi.... comic books!

---------------------------------------------------------------

Star Wars Omnibus - A Long Time Ago... Vol. 1 (digital)
Dark Horse, 2010, 493 pages
This volume collects Marvel Star Wars issues 1-27

Star Wars Omnibus - A Long Time Ago... Vol. 2 (digital)
Dark Horse, 2010, 458 pages
This volume collects Marvel Star Wars issues 28-49 and Star Wars King Size Annual 1

Star Wars Omnibus - A Long Time Ago... Vol. 3 (digital)
Dark Horse, 2011, 472 pages
This volume collects Marvel Star Wars issues 50-67 and Star Wars King Size Annual 2

Star Wars Omnibus - A Long Time Ago... Vol. 4 (digital)
Dark Horse, 2011, 554 pages
This volume collects Marvel Star Wars issues 68-85, Star Wars King Size Annual 3 and Star Wars Return of the Jedi 1-4

Star Wars Omnibus - A Long Time Ago... Vol. 5 (digital)
Dark Horse, 2012, 549 pages
This volume collects Marvel Star Wars issues 86-107
